column5: Got this pic in an email from my cousin who lives in Yellowknife. Lets just say I'm jealous...  Hasn't even hit puberty and he's already crushed my PB Pike.  -Ben

nice fish!  Is it strung on rope or is that the standard fishing line they use out there lol.
